  "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "The `state` member variable exposed by the BaseController is mutable and can be modified externally. Direct state modification shouldn't be allowed since it bypasses notification. The `state` variable should be made readonly so that it's immutable and can only be modified by calling `update` or an exposed API method that modifies state internally. ",
